response.original_title: Raven’s Restler Rescue: EP 1 – Merry Men
response.overview: In this edition, Raven grabs two young upstarts currently struggling with a gimmick called La Cosa Nostra and transforms them into a couple of dashing, sexually ambiguous swashbucklers.  Of course the real test is always hearing a crowd pop. Will it happen for Raven and these Merry Men in Tights?  Follow Raven every step of the way and Find out if Raven’s efforts were a rescue or a wreck!
response.title: Raven’s Restler Rescue: EP 1 – Merry Men
